sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Next.js UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis

    User->>UI: Email + password girer
    UI->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>DB: User'ı email ile bul
    alt User bulunamadı
        DB-->>API: Null
        API-->>UI: 401 Unauthorized
        UI-->>User: "Email veya şifre hatalı"
    else User bulundu
        DB-->>API: User kaydı
        API->>API: Argon2id verify
        alt Şifre yanlış
            API-->>UI: 401 Unauthorized
            UI-->>User: "Email veya şifre hatalı"
        else Şifre doğru
            API->>API: RS256 Access Token üret (15dk)
            API->>API: RS256 Refresh Token üret (7gün)
            API->>DB: refresh_tokens tablosuna kaydet
            API->>Redis: refresh_token:{jti} → user_id (TTL 7gün)
            API-->>UI: 200 OK + httpOnly cookies
            Note over API,UI: access_token cookie (15dk)<br/>refresh_token cookie (7gün, path=/auth/refresh)
            UI-->>User: Dashboard'a yönlendir
        end
    end